    "ts": "1720660543.429949",
    "client_msg_id": "ea812aae-b8d6-471e-bdb9-5540d15670ff",
    "text": "Here's the Lua code skeleton corresponding to that drawing. The ellipses are the protrusions:\n\n```for line_index, line in array.each(State.lines, State.screen_top.line) do\n\tif line.mode == 'text' then\n\t\tlocal initpos = 1\n\t\tif line_index == State.screen_top.line then\n\t\t\t-- top screen line\n\t\t\tinitpos = State.screen_top.pos\n\t\tend\n\t\tfor pos, char in utf8chars(line.data, initpos) do\n\t\t\tif char:match('%s') then\n\t\t\t\tif line_wrap_at_word_boundary(State) then\n\t\t\t\t\t...\n\t\t\t\telse\n\t\t\t\t\t...\n\t\t\t\tend\n\t\t\telse\n\t\t\t\tif x+w &gt; State.right then\n\t\t\t\t\t...\n\t\t\t\telse\n\t\t\t\t\t...\n\t\t\t\tend\n\t\t\tend\n\t\tend\n\telse  -- drawing\n\t\t...\n\tend\nend```\n",
    "team": "T5TCAFTA9",
    "thread_ts": "1720660021.938839",
    "parent_user_id": "UCUSW7WVD",
    "blocks": [
      {
        "type": "rich_text",
        "block_id": "gwAzp",
        "elements": [
          {
            "type": "rich_text_section",
            "elements": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Here's the Lua code skeleton corresponding to that drawing. The ellipses are the protrusions:\n\n"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "rich_text_preformatted",
            "elements": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "for line_index, line in array.each(State.lines, State.screen_top.line) do\n\tif line.mode == 'text' then\n\t\tlocal initpos = 1\n\t\tif line_index == State.screen_top.line then\n\t\t\t-- top screen line\n\t\t\tinitpos = State.screen_top.pos\n\t\tend\n\t\tfor pos, char in utf8chars(line.data, initpos) do\n\t\t\tif char:match('%s') then\n\t\t\t\tif line_wrap_at_word_boundary(State) then\n\t\t\t\t\t...\n\t\t\t\telse\n\t\t\t\t\t...\n\t\t\t\tend\n\t\t\telse\n\t\t\t\tif x+w > State.right then\n\t\t\t\t\t...\n\t\t\t\telse\n\t\t\t\t\t...\n\t\t\t\tend\n\t\t\tend\n\t\tend\n\telse  -- drawing\n\t\t...\n\tend\nend"
