    "client_msg_id": "E86F6911-4247-4F4E-9A18-D8956CFB07AA",
    "text": "That shape doesn’t mean anything to me yet, but I love that it means something to you and that if we were to talk about it, it would probably become a useful artifact for us both to refer to as we forget the details…\n\nI think there’s potential for semantics to be layered onto a diagram like that, in a way that can be maintained as the design evolves. It reminds me of <http://tinlizzie.org/dbjr/high_contrast.html|http://tinlizzie.org/dbjr/high_contrast.html>",
